# Privacy Policy for Adv.KVStore

**Last Updated**: April 12, 2026

## Data Collection

**Adv.KVStore does not collect, transmit, or store any telemetry, analytics, or personal data.**

All processing occurs locally within your YouTrack instance.

## External Services

**The app does not contact any external services.** All key-value storage operations are performed entirely within the YouTrack app runtime using YouTrack's extension properties.

## Data Processing

- The app stores key-value data in YouTrack extension properties (issue, project, and global scope)
- Stored data is accessible only through the app's HTTP API and admin panel
- No stored data, user data, or credentials are logged or transmitted to third parties

## Contact

For privacy-related questions, contact: apps@mag1.cc
